        <item>
            <title>日本 Pizza Hut 推全球首个 AI Pizza   全系列披萨产品芝士量升级到 130%</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/20/pizza-hut/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=pizza-hut</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/20/pizza-hut/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 20 Oct 2024 09:00:39 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pizza Hut]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1270275</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日本 Pizza Hut 宣布推出史上初首个「AI Pizza」，将全国范围内的 Pizza 产品芝士量增加至 130%。原来今次宣传背后有真正用到 AI 技术，他们开发了「AI 味觉感测器」硬件，利用 AI 分析 Pizza 味道、口感。「AI Pizza」将于 10 月 21 日起在全国门店上架，芝士增量但价格保持不变。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270281" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ts1648348_202410171_-1-622x580.jpg" alt="" width="622" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ts1648348_202410171_-1-622x580.jpg 622w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ts1648348_202410171_-1.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 622px" /></p><p>Pizza Hut 采用了由庆应义塾大学研发的 AI 味觉感测器「レオ」（Rio）来测定最佳芝士量。Rio 透过电气信号模拟味蕾，利用神经网络将甜、咸、酸、苦、鲜味的感官体验数据化，让味道的分析不再受人体状况或季节变化影响。经过一系列测试，Rio 发现芝士增加 130% 至 140% 之间的量能达至最佳味觉。然而当试食者试食 140% 芝士的披萨时，六款披萨的味道平衡出现了问题，因此最终选择将芝士量增加至 130%。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270282" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/l_ts1648348_20241017-694x427.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="427" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/l_ts1648348_20241017-694x427.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/l_ts1648348_20241017.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>此次 AI 驱动的芝士升级，Pizza Hut 同时推出了一套生成 AI 制作的宣传影片，搭配「AI Pizza」的背景音乐，以宣传这个最新的 AI Pizza。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270283" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/l_ts1648348_20241017-1-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/l_ts1648348_20241017-1-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/l_ts1648348_20241017-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_33896"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yzSc9WXYFgQ?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yzSc9WXYFgQ">YouTube</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/20/pizza-hut/ai/">日本 Pizza Hut 推全球首个 AI Pizza   全系列披萨产品芝士量升级到 130%</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
